    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.4,
      "text": "Excuse me sir, sir real quick guys, we said no, thank you real quick. We grow a channel to 18 million followers"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.4,
      "end": 9.4,
      "text": "Get the fuck out of here. How you doing man? Super familiar. I had to be the billionaires. Yeah, that's right"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.4,
      "end": 12.7,
      "text": "How did you get rich? Investing in what type of businesses? You have 30 seconds?"
    },
    {
      "start": 12.9,
      "end": 16.1,
      "text": "Yeah, okay, I came to this country when I was five years old first-generation immigrant"
    },
    {
      "start": 16.1,
      "end": 21.0,
      "text": "We came to this country with nothing in one generation my parents chased and lived the American dream"
    },
    {
      "start": 21.0,
      "end": 23.6,
      "text": "I joined the Marines that was my responsibility after the Marines"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.6,
      "end": 26.1,
      "text": "I have 120 companies right now that across your companies"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.1,
      "end": 29.2,
      "text": "What was the most amount of money you made this year across the board billions?"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.2,
      "end": 34.3,
      "text": "You can't fail when you know this is God's plan. You believe in God, of course. Who is your God?"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.7,
      "end": 40.7,
      "text": "God you believe in Jesus you a Christian? I am you are yeah, how important has that faith been for you throughout your career?"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.8,
      "end": 42.4,
      "text": "I'll tell you this every day"
    },
    {
      "start": 42.4,
      "end": 46.4,
      "text": "I grow deeper in my faith and that doesn't mean I don't wrestle with God in fact the service"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.4,
      "end": 47.7,
      "text": "I went to a couple weeks ago"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.7,
      "end": 53.9,
      "text": "They talked about by definition if you're wrestling with God you are closer to God if you are accepting everything that you hear"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.9,
      "end": 57.4,
      "text": "You're not questioning in some way. You're not wrestling with God. You read a lot of books"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.4,
      "end": 59.9,
      "text": "Yeah, I went through the deep deep spiritual journey man"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.9,
      "end": 63.1,
      "text": "What was the number one book that changed your life? I come back to the alchemist"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.1,
      "end": 69.0,
      "text": "Alchemist entrepreneurship is modern-day alchemy you are taking an idea something that doesn't exist and you're making it real everything"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.0,
      "end": 73.4,
      "text": "Everything you're doing right now. This was an idea and it's real now modern-day alchemy the alchemist"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.4,
      "end": 78.2,
      "text": "How do you know 41 if mean you died tomorrow and you had one more message to leave with the younger generation"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.2,
      "end": 82.0,
      "text": "What would that be? I'm gonna tell you right now the number one regret of the dying is"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.0,
      "end": 86.4,
      "text": "I wish I'd had the courage to live a life true to myself not the life others expected of me"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.4,
      "end": 90.6,
      "text": "How about we don't wait to be on our deathbed to actually have the courage to live a life?"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.7,
      "end": 95.4,
      "text": "We care about I hope I'm here a lot longer, but if not, I feel grateful for every day. I wake up brother"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.4,
      "end": 100.2,
      "text": "You have a basic advice. I mean that was excellent man, and I connect with all the millionaires and billionaires at any of you"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.2,
      "end": 102.1,
      "text": "Can I get your contact? Yeah, absolutely. Yeah"
